===Noun===
'''[[olive]] [[branch]]'''

#(''biblical'') the branch of an olive tree brought by a [[dove]] to [[Noah's ark]] as a [[sign]] that the [[flood]] was [[subsiding]]
#a similar branch as an [[emblem]] of [[peace]]
#any [[symbol]] of peace, or an [[offering]] to an [[adversary]] to show [[good will]] and in the [[hope]] of securing peace

